{"tid":312213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「翠如BB股」再插17% 年內暴跌98%","createTime":"2017-07-07T09:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T09:55:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03bbcf17e1f3e0fcfebe0ce6ab0febd1058a2c3c","tid":312213,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499331684_fb49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499331684_fb49.jpg&h=7578cd98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n細價股爆煲陰霾未散，「翠如BB股」聯旺（8217）流血不止，今日再挫16.7%，跌至0.5元，成交6,510萬元。該股今周四個交易，日日插水超過一成，四日累挫47%。<br />\n<br />\n聯旺今年1月曾單日炒高兩成，以26元創上市高位，股價隨即開始「卸妝」，反覆下瀉，加上細價股連環跌一役，現價較今年高位大挫98%，勁低殘。黃翠如爸爸黃永華持有4.68億股，持股比例37.5%，以聯旺現價0.5元計，其持股市值僅得2.34億港元，身家半年蒸發119億。"},{"pid":"9bce26ab4f72adeb472fc4d61ba45805f5208bbb","tid":312213,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日收 0.4 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181fcfbddce43bba66156602a9f89ff8b6c1957d","tid":312213,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cfe8c756efc9af334cac03de2f028f7e147b8d2","tid":312213,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e973d73323e5d97fe5158c9fe9bf6de5936f53d7","tid":312213,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日收 0.4 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\